	"readme": "## svelte-media-query ([npm](https://www.npmjs.com/package/svelte-media-query), [demo](https://svelte.dev/repl/26eb44932920421da01e2e21539494cd))\nCSS media queries in svelte.\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\nnpm i svelte-media-query\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```html\n<script>\n    import MediaQuery from \"svelte-media-query\";\n</script>\n\n<MediaQuery query=\"(min-width: 1281px)\" let:matches>\n    {#if matches}\n    <div class=\"root default\">\n        default\n    </div>\n    {/if}\n</MediaQuery>\n\n<MediaQuery query=\"(min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 1280px)\" let:matches>\n    {#if matches}\n    <div class=\"root tablet\">\n        tablet\n    </div>\n    {/if}\n</MediaQuery>\n\n<MediaQuery query=\"(max-width: 480px)\" let:matches>\n    {#if matches}\n    <div class=\"root mobile\">\n        mobile\n    </div>\n    {/if}\n</MediaQuery>\n```\n",
